<DocsLayout title="Delete Account" section="Account Information">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    This guide explains how to delete your account and user data from Field Promax,
    including instructions for web and mobile apps, and how to export data before closure.
  </p>
  <p>
    Cancelling your account is straightforward — send us an email or give us a call,
    and we'll take care of the rest.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>
  <p>To delete your account and user data, contact us:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@fieldpromax.com</li>
    <li><strong>Phone:</strong> 888-249-9201</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="callout callout-warning">
    <p>
      <strong>Important:</strong> Only the main administrator of the account may request cancellation.
      Your data will be permanently deleted within 90 days of the request.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Mobile App Data</h2>

  <h3>Android & iOS</h3>
  <p>Both <strong>Field Promax 2</strong> and <strong>Field Promax Plus</strong> apps are developed by Field Promax.</p>

  <h4>Clear Location Data</h4>
  <ol>
    <li>Log in to the app</li>
    <li>Click the menu</li>
    <li>Select <strong>Privacy</strong> → <strong>Clear location data</strong></li>
  </ol>

  <h4>Delete User Information</h4>
  <p>
    Email and phone numbers can be deleted by the main administrator:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>Log in to the <strong>Field Promax web application</strong></li>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Users</strong></li>
    <li>Select the user and click delete</li>
  </ol>

  <h4>Delete Images and Documents</h4>
  <p>
    Delete any images or documents by going into each work order where they were uploaded.
  </p>

  <h2>Export Data Before Closure</h2>

  <h3>Export Reports</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Reports</strong></li>
    <li>Select a report and choose the date range</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Export Excel Copy</strong></li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Download PDFs</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Navigate to the item (quote, job, or invoice)</li>
    <li>Select <strong>Actions</strong> → <strong>Download PDF</strong></li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only the <strong>main administrator</strong> can request account cancellation</li>
    <li>You receive an <strong>email notification</strong> when data is deleted</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Field Promax does not share data with third-party organizations.
    For more details, see our <a href="https://www.fieldpromax.com/privacy-policy-2/" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Export important data</strong> before requesting account deletion.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Download PDFs</strong> of invoices and work orders you may need later.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
